What can you find here?
-----------------------

- the BioSecure tool used to evaluate the performance of 
a biometric verification system.
- a documentation which explains how to use the tool.


First step
----------

To begin, I advise you to read the document stored in 
/doc directory.


Short description of each directory
-----------------------------------

- doc: documentation which explains how to use the tool.

- src: source code.


Questions
---------

If you have questions about the use of the tool, you can 
contact the next person:
Aurelien Mayoue: aurelien.mayoue@int-evry.fr
